description:
This is a 33 minute workout called '30 MIN FULL BODY WORKOUT || At-Home Pilates (No Equipment)' from the channel Move With Nicole.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Pilates.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Masterclass Workout and The Foundation Builder vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate and Challenging.
